Package: pd-pkg-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: git-buildpackage, devscripts
Description: Tools for building Debian Pd packages
 This package contains useful tools for building and maintaining Debian packages
 for Pure Data libraries.
 It's targeted at the Debian Multimedia Maintainers Team, subsection Pure Data.
 This package currently includes:
    * CDBS classes for building packages for pd (and flavour puredata)


